ent-PosterLegitRipleyCertified = сертифицированный Рипли
    .desc = By god, he's forkli- I mean, Ripley certified...
ent-PosterLegitKillersClinic = клиника убийц
    .desc = A clinic, for killers? Apparently, you get complimentary music played while you're treated.
ent-PosterlegitLawPoster = реклама юридических услуг
    .desc = A poster advertising the eponimous Butcher A. Hemmel law firm, great for beating murder charges!
ent-PosterContrabandFentsAndCo = шаттлостроительная компания «Fents & Co»
    .desc = A poster shaped like a shuttle with the name of some totally illegal company on it, how odd.
ent-PosterContrabandWantedClown = Розыск: клоун
    .desc = A wanted poster for a Clown. Thanks to the mask, you have no idea who.
ent-PosterContrabandWantedFreak = Розыск: Фрик
    .desc = A wanted poster for Freak the Clown. It's outdated, you think.
ent-PosterContrabandWantedIan = Розыск: Иан
    .desc = A wanted poster for Ian the Corgi. What sins has he committed? What unseen cruelty lies behind those empty eyes?
ent-PosterContrabandWantedJohnToe = Розыск: Джон Тоу
