    .desc = An old poster for the derelict Comitas Systems company. Supposedly, there is a message hidden in this poster.
ent-PosterContrabandWaffleCorpTwo = Waffle Corp: Affordable, and Practical.
    .desc = A poster for Waffle Corp. Why does a waffle company make firearms...?
ent-PosterLegit247 = 24/7
    .desc = Open 24 hours a spaceday, seven days a spaceweek!
ent-PosterLegitNanoTrasenFancy = NanoTrasen
    .desc = Made of the same cheap aluminium as all the other signs, but with a glossy finish!
ent-PosterContrabandThunderdome = Thunderdome
    .desc = Guaranteed bloodbath in the Thunderdooooooome!
ent-PosterLegitPlasma = Plasma and You
